1580849: Reflection Question:
ReflectÂ  on how design thinking is relevant in your chosen career trajectory.

This is my essay about design thinking and how I will use problem solving and problem finding in my future career trajectory. Being a computer scientist, critical thinking is very important. Teamwork, leadership, and project planning are also very important. The focus of a computer scientist is people-centered or user-centered, depending on the project. Projects include lost of brainstorming, solution generation, decision making, and of course project management.

This is my essay about how I will use critical thinking, creative thinking, and design thinking in my career trajectory as an engineer. In my daily life I will consider people centered, user centered, and human centered perspectives in my design. I will need to empathize, problem solve, and provide leadership as well. I will use critical thinking and creative thinking daily as well.
